column2: CHAPTER III.
PHYSICAL CHARACTERISTICS.
BEAUTY.
If a person is very handsome, it is a sign that he will have one of the infectious diseases of childhood (measles, whooping cough, etc.) more than once. _Massachusetts._
column3: If a person is very handsome, it is a sign that he will have one of the infectious diseases of childhood (measles, whooping cough, etc) more than once. underscore Massachusetts.underscore

column2: DIMPLE.
Dimple in chin. Devil within. _Chestertown, Md._
column3: Dimple in chin. Devil within. underscore Chestertown, m d.underscore

column2: A dimple in the chin is lucky.
column3: A dimple in the chin is lucky.

column2: Some say "it shows you're no fool."
column3: Some say "it shows you're no fool."

column2: A dimple is the mark left by the angel's finger in turning up the face to kiss it when asleep. _Pennsylvania._
column3: A dimple is the mark left by the angel's finger in turning up the face to kiss it when asleep. underscore Pennsylvania.underscore

column2: EARS.
Small ears indicate that a person is stingy.
column3: Small ears indicate that a person is stingy.

column2: Large ones show that he is generous. _General._
column3: Large ones show that he is generous. underscore General.underscore

column2: Large ears are a mark of a liar.
column3: Large ears are a mark of a liar.

column2: Small ears show that one is truthful. _Boston, Mass._
column3: Small ears show that one is truthful. underscore Boston, Mass.underscore

column2: Long, slim ears are a sign that you will steal. _Chestertown, Md._
column3: Long, slim ears are a sign that you will steal. underscore Chestertown, m d.underscore

column2: If the protuberance behind the ear is large, it indicates generosity. _Massachusetts._
column3: If the protuberance behind the ear is large, it indicates generosity. underscore Massachusetts.underscore

column2: EYES AND EYEBROWS.
Hazel eyes betoken a good disposition. _Boston, Mass._
column3: Hazel eyes betoken a good disposition. underscore Boston, Mass.underscore

column2: If your eyebrows meet, you will be rich. _Somerville and Bedford, Mass._
column3: If your eyebrows meet, you will be rich. underscore Somerville and Bedford, Mass.underscore

column2: A well-known children's rhyme runs:--
Blue-eye beauty, do your mammy's duty! Black eye, pick a pie, Run around and tell a lie! Gray-eye greedy gut Eat all the world up! _General in the United States._
column3: Blue eye beauty, do your mammy's duty! Black eye, pick a pie, Run around and tell a lie! Gray eye greedy gut Eat all the world up! underscore General in the United States.underscore

column2: If the eyebrows meet, one is ill-tempered. _General in the United States._
column3: If the eyebrows meet, one is ill tempered. underscore General in the United States.underscore

column2: If the eyebrows are far apart, you will live away from home; if near together, you will live near home, or at home. _Massachusetts._
column3: If the eyebrows are far apart, you will live away from home; if near together, you will live near home, or at home. underscore Massachusetts.underscore

column2: Heavy eyebrows are a sign of long life. _Lawrence, Mass._
column3: Heavy eyebrows are a sign of long life. underscore Lawrence, Mass.underscore

column2: FINGER-NAILS.
Always keep your nails clean and you will be rich. _Peabody, Mass._
column3: Always keep your nails clean and you will be rich. underscore Peabody, Mass.underscore

column2: A white spot in the nail, when it comes, means a present.
column3: A white spot in the nail, when it comes, means a present.

column2: You get the present when it grows to the end and is cut. _Boston, Mass._
column3: You get the present when it grows to the end and is cut. underscore Boston, Mass.underscore

column2: White spots on the nails of the left hand denote the number of lies one has told. _Maine and Central Illinois._
column3: White spots on the nails of the left hand denote the number of lies one has told. underscore Maine and Central Illinois.underscore

column2: Count on finger-nail spots:--
Friends, Foes, Money, Beaux.
Begin with the first nail spotted, and the noun falling to the last nail thus marked gives the sign. _Deerfield, Mass._
column3: Begin with the first nail spotted, and the noun falling to the last nail thus marked gives the sign. underscore Deerfield, Mass.underscore

column2: Another formula:--
(First finger) a friend, (Second finger) a foe, (Third finger) a gift, (Fourth finger) a beau, (Fifth finger) a journey to go. _Mansfield, O._
column3: (First finger) a friend, (Second finger) a foe, (Third finger) a gift, (Fourth finger) a beau, (Fifth finger) a journey to go. underscore Mansfield, o underscore

column2: An almost identical variant is found in Prince Edward Island.
column3: An almost identical variant is found in Prince Edward Island.

column2: FOOT.
If your instep is high enough to have water flow under it, you are of good descent. _Brookline, Mass._
column3: If your instep is high enough to have water flow under it, you are of good descent. underscore Brookline, Mass.underscore

column2: A mole on the sole of the left foot means trouble and hardships during life. _Boston, Mass._
column3: A mole on the sole of the left foot means trouble and hardships during life. underscore Boston, Mass.underscore

column2: FOREHEAD.
If there is a blue vein in the child's forehead extending down upon the nose, it is one of the surest signs of early death. _Maine and Massachusetts._
column3: If there is a blue vein in the child's forehead extending down upon the nose, it is one of the surest signs of early death. underscore Maine and Massachusetts.underscore

column2: Vertical wrinkles in the brow show the number of husbands one will have.
column3: Vertical wrinkles in the brow show the number of husbands one will have.

column2: Horizontal ones show the number of children. _Northern Ohio._
column3: Horizontal ones show the number of children. underscore Northern Ohio.underscore

column2: HAIR.
Coarse hair indicates good nature; fine hair quick temper. _Northern Ohio._
column3: Coarse hair indicates good nature; fine hair quick temper. underscore Northern Ohio.underscore

column2: Red hair indicates a "spit-fire." _Massachusetts and Chestertown, Md._
column3: Red hair indicates a "spit fire." underscore Massachusetts and Chestertown, m d.underscore

column2: Beware of that man, Be he friend or brother, Whose hair is one color And moustache another. _Portland, Me._
column3: Beware of that man, Be he friend or brother, Whose hair is one color And moustache another. underscore Portland, Me.underscore

column2: The color of the hair growing on the neck indicates the color of the hair of one's future husband.
column3: The color of the hair growing on the neck indicates the color of the hair of one's future husband.

column2: A single white hair means genius; it must not be pulled out.
column3: A single white hair means genius; it must not be pulled out.

column2: If you pull out a white hair, two will come in its place. _Somewhat general in the United States._
column3: If you pull out a white hair, two will come in its place. underscore Somewhat general in the United States.underscore

column2: Hair growing upon the upper lip of a woman means riches. _Boston, Mass._
column3: Hair growing upon the upper lip of a woman means riches. underscore Boston, Mass.underscore

column2: The point formed by the hair growing on the forehead is called "A widow's peak." _Eastern Massachusetts._
column3: The point formed by the hair growing on the forehead is called "A widow's peak." underscore Eastern Massachusetts.underscore

column2: When a woman's hair parts where it should not, it is a sure sign she will be a widow. _Springfield, Mass._
column3: When a woman's hair parts where it should not, it is a sure sign she will be a widow. underscore Springfield, Mass.underscore

column2: Draw a single hair from the head strongly between the thumb and finger-nail.
column3: Draw a single hair from the head strongly between the thumb and finger nail.

column2: If it curls up, you are proud. _St.
column3: If it curls up, you are proud. underscore st

column2: John, N.B., and Prince Edward Island._
column3: john, n b, and Prince Edward Island.underscore

column2: The same result indicates that you are cross. _Cape Breton._
column3: The same result indicates that you are cross. underscore Cape Breton.underscore

column2: Hairy arms mean wealth. _Northern Ohio._
column3: Hairy arms mean wealth. underscore Northern Ohio.underscore

column2: Hairy arms mean strength. _General in the United States._
column3: Hairy arms mean strength. underscore General in the United States.underscore

column2: Scrape the finger-nail and the thumb-nail along a hair, and if, by the third time, it curls up, the owner is high-tempered. _Boston, Mass._
column3: Scrape the finger nail and the thumb nail along a hair, and if, by the third time, it curls up, the owner is high tempered. underscore Boston, Mass.underscore

column2: Put some of your hair in the fire.
column3: Put some of your hair in the fire.

column2: If it burns slowly you will have a long life.
column3: If it burns slowly you will have a long life.

column2: If quickly, a short one. _Chestertown, Md._
column3: If quickly, a short one. underscore Chestertown, m d.underscore

column2: HAND.
A straight line in the palm of the hand is an omen of early death. _Massachusetts._
column3: A straight line in the palm of the hand is an omen of early death. underscore Massachusetts.underscore

column2: The letter formed by the veins on the inside of the wrist is the initial of the name of the future husband or wife. _St.
column3: The letter formed by the veins on the inside of the wrist is the initial of the name of the future husband or wife. underscore st

column2: John, N.B._
A person with an initial in his hand will be very fortunate in selecting a companion for life. _Alabama._
column3: A person with an initial in his hand will be very fortunate in selecting a companion for life. underscore Alabama.underscore

column2: In clasping your own hand, you put uppermost either your right or your left thumb.
column3: In clasping your own hand, you put uppermost either your right or your left thumb.

column2: If the former, you are to rule; _vice versa_, you yield. _Brookline, Mass._
column3: If the former, you are to rule; underscore vice versa underscore, you yield. underscore Brookline, Mass.underscore

column2: If the thumb sticks up in the closed fist, you are either capable or honest, probably the latter, as thieves are said to double theirs in. _New England._
column3: If the thumb sticks up in the closed fist, you are either capable or honest, probably the latter, as thieves are said to double theirs in. underscore New England.underscore

column2: If you cannot make your thumb and one finger meet around your wrist, you are a glutton. _Province of Quebec._
column3: If you cannot make your thumb and one finger meet around your wrist, you are a glutton. underscore Province of Quebec.underscore

column2: If you cannot touch the tips of your little finger and first finger together behind the two middle fingers, on both hands, then you will not marry the man you want to marry. _Province of Quebec._
column3: If you cannot touch the tips of your little finger and first finger together behind the two middle fingers, on both hands, then you will not marry the man you want to marry. underscore Province of Quebec.underscore

column2: Clasp your fingers, and if the right thumb lap over the left you were born in the daytime.
column3: Clasp your fingers, and if the right thumb lap over the left you were born in the daytime.

column2: If the left overlap, you were born at night.
column3: If the left overlap, you were born at night.

column2: The number of folds on your wrist as you bend your hand shows the number of thirties you are to live. _Massachusetts._
column3: The number of folds on your wrist as you bend your hand shows the number of thirties you are to live. underscore Massachusetts.underscore

column2: If the ends of the fingers are capable of being bent far back, it indicates a thief.
column3: If the ends of the fingers are capable of being bent far back, it indicates a thief.

column2: MOLES.
A mole on the eyebrow denotes that one will be hanged.
column3: A mole on the eyebrow denotes that one will be hanged.

column2: On the ear it denotes that he will be drowned. _Chestertown, Md._
column3: On the ear it denotes that he will be drowned. underscore Chestertown, m d.underscore

column2: Mole above breath Means wealth.
Moles on the neck, Money by the peck. _Prince Edward Island and Northern Ohio._
column3: Moles on the neck, Money by the peck. underscore Prince Edward Island and Northern Ohio.underscore

column2: A mole on the neck indicates that its owner will be hanged. _Boston, Mass._
column3: A mole on the neck indicates that its owner will be hanged. underscore Boston, Mass.underscore

column2: A mole on the side of the neck means a death by hanging. _Central Maine._
column3: A mole on the side of the neck means a death by hanging. underscore Central Maine.underscore
